item.title: CVE-2018-0649|2024-08-05T03:35:48.946Z -- canon%20it%20solutions%20inc. -- the%20installers%20of%20multiple%20canon%20it%20solutions%20inc.%20software%20programs
item.description: Untrusted search path vulnerability in the installers of multiple Canon IT Solutions Inc. software programs (ESET Smart Security Premium, ESET Internet Security, ESET Smart Security, ESET NOD32 Antivirus, DESlock+ Pro, and CompuSec (all programs except packaged ones)) allows an attacker to gain privileges via a Trojan horse DLL in an unspecified directory.
